Text.val: 17.09.2012 SH SCR17538 Changed Unicode fields back to alpha where SQL is used

ExpSyntax.val: 'CREATE TABLE QTEMP/MGJOBI (JOB CHAR (132 ) NOT NULL WITH DEFAULT)'
'CPYSPLF FILE(QPDSPJOB) TOFILE(QTEMP/MGJOBI) JOB(*) SPLNBR(*LAST) TOMBR(*FIRST) MBROPT(*REPLACE) '

SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT SUBSTR(JOB , 2 , 10), SUBSTR(JOB , 14, 10), SUBSTR(JOB , 50, 5), SUBSTR(JOB , 54, 9), SUBSTR(JOB , 65, 2) FROM qtemp/MGJOBI WHERE SUBSTR(JOB , 88, 1) = '*' FOR READ ONLY WITH NC OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS
